求<br />\n<br />\n次次都係被遺棄  我都好攰</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係 狠心講句<br />\n分咗手唔會祝人幸福快樂<br />\n只會希望你嘅下一個永遠都唔會比我好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b3413b3bf1310410dc684de958438f76756700","tid":19350,"uid":44368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:56:01.000Z","msg":"當你適應曬同呢個人一齊 再去適應新一個 真係好煩"},{"pid":"031a0b0369a8f2cfa5938de7170ae0532292c782","tid":19350,"uid":44368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:56:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 重新識人好攰，唔想識完但最後俾人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d6a0fb51dbcef419cbf4b2307014ef8a9684e4","tid":19350,"uid":44368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:57:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>要花時間了解人 又花時間等人了解自己 真係好麻煩<br />\n唔好話伴侶 宜家係連認識新朋友都做唔到<br />\n覺得一個人就做到既野何必要多一個人 維繫一段關係真係好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n全中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 花時間了解人但人地唔了解自己，好似自作多情咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你好想去了解一個人 但人地完全唔想去了解你個下 真係仆曬街"},{"pid":"b186a026096079d91b0870f16911254344433b7d","tid":19350,"uid":44368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:57:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>要花時間了解人 又花時間等人了解自己 真係好麻煩<br />\n唔好話伴侶 宜家係連認識新朋友都做唔到<br />\n覺得一個人就做到既野何必要多一個人 維繫一段關係真係好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n全中<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 花時間了解人但人地唔了解自己，好似自作多情咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當人地同你講 「點解你可以咁明白我」 嗰陣 真